{"tid":2038003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CCTVB：受疫情影響本地廣告大減實屬正常 集團為本地廣告界龍頭不怕網民威嚇","createTime":"2020-05-27T09:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T10:16:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7260a8889a45fa1ab322818b9332471eea395a","tid":2038003,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"電視廣播：本地廣告業務佔總收入已降至53%<br />\n2020-05-27 HKT 17:32<br />\n<br />\n電視廣播副主席兼行政總裁李寶安表示，新型肺炎疫情衝擊零售、娛樂及展覽等行業，對公司廣告大幅減少並不意外，但相信承受過衝擊後，市場一定會恢復。<br />\n<br />\n對於有市民自去年起發起杯葛與集團合作的廣告商，李寶安說，對集團影響有限，雖然社會事件令不少公司及廣告商承受壓力，但集團在香港的廣告市佔率高達85%，業務較受經濟及商業環境影響。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，旗下節目收視率近期已經回升不少，令客戶有信心參與合作，集團近年亦積極發展廣告以外的業務，本地廣告業務佔總收入已降至53%，未來會繼續透過OTT及電子商務等較穩定方式增加收入。<br />\n<br />\n他提到，公司去年已經裁減部分員工，電子商貿等業務更會增加人手，暫未再有裁員計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528697-20200527.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528697-20200527.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32d8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=ffc53a7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528697-20200527.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=43fedd7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528697-20200527.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ef55d50f2453d11a9de38d76072cdc34956889f9","tid":2038003,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d6f5e193165a964c570c4b150388895e8f64fc","tid":2038003,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:48